reviewText: I've had this for a while and although it is taken from a VHS tape it's a good show.  I really love the version of "Street Hassle" from this concert.

this has been a bootleg (from TV) for about a decade.
Nice show but - my boot is the same quality- spanish subtitles and all.
Kind of hoping it was some of the 'midnight special' stuff - w. wolfman jack - the street hassle/ growing up in public stuff he did for that TV  show- i have it crappy audio  but someday it might surface
